00:22:45,899 --> 00:22:48,367
Go ahead, frisby.

458
00:22:48,402 --> 00:22:49,985
Make a speech.

459
00:22:50,020 --> 00:22:51,870
I've been waiting all day
for this.

460
00:22:51,905 --> 00:22:53,739
Yeah, come
on, frisby!

461
00:22:53,774 --> 00:22:55,624
