up to the moon, huh?

465
00:23:02,532 --> 00:23:05,634
Now, you know,
you ain't very far wrong.

466
00:23:05,669 --> 00:23:10,005
Do you know who them fellas
was out there in that car?

467
00:23:10,040 --> 00:23:11,890
Well, i'll tell
you who they was.

